{"tid":922054,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"除左上司同老細，有冇一個同事，你覺得冇左佢就perfect池？","createTime":"2018-11-30T05:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T06:30:24.000Z","uid":169972,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8e18aea61a7ef5bd089a0ca8febd8a81a2b1c4","tid":922054,"uid":169972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:02:58.000Z","msg":"我有個女同事好重機心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成日都係到主張周圍打好關係，<br />\n佢覺得好似全世界（包括我）都要好似佢咁同任何人都要打好關係<br />\n成間公司咁多人，我點得閒做到個個我都要去拍佢馬屁撩佢傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係佢出糧比我，又唔係佢請我<br />\n又話咩IT係全公司電腦既重心，一定要打好，如果唔係人地唔幫我地整<br />\n計我話佢根本就係到姣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同另一個同事都覺得佢行為不檢，<br />\n同事都同我傾，話佢係咪對人有意思呀<br />\n同個IT人講野就咁嬌嗲，同我地講又另一把聲<br />\n<br />\n佢仲好自作聰明自以為是<br />\n以為自己叻少少就代表佢精通全部野<br />\n有次佢問我整咩，<br />\n我話學點印野係膠片上面，<br />\n佢話同普通印野冇分別洗乜學，問題佢根本唔知用乜膠印，佢好意思話咪即係用尼過膠D膠片Lo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地都係打工仔虛心D咪算lo<br />\n點解要係到懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有佢真係好L八卦，唔關佢事既野都要豎起隻耳尼聽<br />\n仲要做得咁明顯，人地傾計佢離遠望住又笑埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最自大就係佢入職先一個月，啱啱入尼就即刻想改人地公司呢樣嗰樣，人地已經做左十幾年，幾時到你一個新人係到改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我咪又係新尼，又唔見我有本事改革？<br />\n<br />\n成日去見其他工，又話辭職同唔撈，講L左咁耐都得個講字<br />\n好想佢快D走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   佢走左就唔會咁多小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cc30662c7b94ef3c27d8f67515f389eb9bc116","tid":922054,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"除左舊老細真係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw依家個個好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421ef1de9f22f7b5ff4e5773204ea2d365ae39d","tid":922054,"uid":10056,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"係有d人係咁屎忽鬼鍾意搞是搞非 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搏人留意佢地咁 實質就好可悲"},{"pid":"72005c2cd301bfdde2aad7e35eb68abeba60b221","tid":922054,"uid":87442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔帶個腦番工的同事 每日啲問題重複又重複 有時一日仲要問多過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff3189a8765ae21efcd55625ca49926d941df07","tid":922054,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72005c2cd301bfdde2aad7e35eb68abeba60b221","tid":922054,"uid":87442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"唔帶個腦番工的同事 每日啲問題重複又重複 有時一日仲要問多過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"sorry囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af92664190a180296a1f1e535f8bd3fb2d4d8397","tid":922054,"uid":2446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"尼你老母"},{"pid":"74c1cf4324f16b48c239da6eef4e5461b8d56ecf","tid":922054,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"個濕鳩肥師奶又冇禮貌<br />\n對客就懶友善<br />\n對同事就成日指揮人做野<br />\n明明大家同level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲鐘意督人背脊<br />\n正一食屎狗黎"},{"pid":"fe82f84696cc7d1e458446dcb237275f401887e5","tid":922054,"uid":103926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T06:22:07.000Z","msg":"身同感受 公司有條撚屌同樓主講既人 一模一樣 濕鳩到喊<br />\n可惜佢刷鞋刷到老細信撚晒佢 做唔撚到d咩 唯有望佢快d死"},{"pid":"23c0ea0a2576ab122beceee7a004fa0e5d7b438e","tid":922054,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b51d7af8f0b082a6c346a4a236a33c4a3534e72","tid":922054,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23c0ea0a2576ab122beceee7a004fa0e5d7b438e","tid":922054,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"冇乜心機做，做錯嘢要人執手尾又唔好意思"}]}